name: Crea redes de apoyo.
description:
In 2015 I was studying with the digital invaders in Saltillo Mexico, and one of out projects was this, 10 steps to become a resilient kid, we want to create a movement against bullying and Bouncying was Our word flag to promote this steps, We do an expo of cartels made by different artist, mine was "Create support networks"  and my generation group phrase was "be the riot" the 13th.

Feeling nostalgic, this piece is dedicated to my friend Jose Luis Salgado Ascencio A.K.A. Capitan Chila. 

Camara carnal te extraño un chingo.
